#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid "[[!meta title=\"Tails report for February, 2014\"]]\n"
msgstr "[[!meta title=\"گزارش فوریه ۲۰۱۴ تیلز\"]]\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Releases\n"
msgstr "انتشارها\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Tails 0.22.1 was released on February 4."
msgstr "تیلز ۰٫۲۲ روز ۴ فوریه منتشر شد."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Metrics\n"
msgstr "متریک‌ها\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Tails has been started more than 222 134 times in February.  This make 7 933 "
"boots a day in average."
msgstr ""
"تیلز بیش از ۲۲۲٫۱۳۴ بار در ماه فوریه راه‌اندازی شد. یعنی به طور متوسط ۷٫۹۳۳ "
"راه‌اندازی در روز."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "453 082 downloads of the OpenPGP signature of Tails ISO. Weird."
msgstr "۴۵۳٫۰۸۲ دانلود امضای اُپن‌پی‌جی‌پی ایزوی تیلز."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "92 reports were received through WhisperBack."
msgstr "۹۲ گزارش از طریق ویسپربک دریافت شدند."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Code\n"
msgstr "کد\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "New features:"
msgstr "ویژگی‌های جدید:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Great progress was made towards better integrated, and more usable, "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/bridge-mode desc=\"support for using Tor "
"bridges\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 5479]]). This implied working with the TBB team "
"to improve Tor Launcher, so that we can start it as a standalone XUL "
"application, instead of as a browser add-on."
msgstr ""
"پیشرفت بسیاری در راه [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/bridge-mode desc=\""
"پشتیبانی استفاده از پل‌های تور\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 5479]]) یکپارچه‌تر و "
"قابل‌استفاده‌تر حاصل شد. این یعنی کار با تیم TBB برای بهتر کردن راه‌انداز "
"تور تا بتوانیم آن را به عنوان یک ابزار مستقل XUL به کار ببریم، نه یک افزونهٔ "
"مرورگر."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[[MAC spoofing support|contribute/design/MAC_address]] was "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/spoof-mac desc=\"completed\"]] and merged "
"([[!tails_ticket 5421]])."
msgstr ""
"[[جا زدن آدرس مک|contribute/design/MAC_address]] was [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/spoof-mac desc=\"کامل\"]] و ادغام شد ([[!tails_ticket 5421]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/6508-incremental-upgrades-phase-four "
"desc=\"Phase four\"]] of incremental upgrades was completed ([[!tails_ticket "
"6508]]), and given it was enabled by default in Tails 0.22.1, most users "
"will see it in action when 0.23 is out."
msgstr ""
"[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/6508-incremental-upgrades-phase-four desc=\""
"فاز چهارم\"]] ارتقاهای تدریجی کامل شد ([[!tails_ticket 6508]]) و با توجه به "
"این که به طور پیش‌فرض در تیلز ۰٫۲۲٫۱ فعال شده بود، بیشتر کاربران آن را پس از "
"انتشار ۰٫۲۳ خواهند دید."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"One may now [[!tails_gitweb_branch_winterfairy bugfix/allow-ibus-start "
"desc=\"start IBus manually\"]] in locales environment where it is disabled "
"by default ([[!tails_ticket 6656]])."
msgstr ""
"حالا می‌توان در محیط بومی [[!tails_gitweb_branch_winterfairy bugfix/allow-"
"ibus-start desc=\"IBus را دستی راه‌اندازی کرد\"]] که در حالت عادی به طور پیش‌"
"فرض غیرفعال است ([[!tails_ticket 6656]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/amd64-kernel desc=\"Ship a 64-bit kernel\"]] "
"in replacement for the 686-pae one ([[!tails_ticket 5456]])."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/amd64-kernel desc=\"گنجاندن یک هستهٔ ۶۴بیتی\""
"]] به جای هستهٔ 686-pae ([[!tails_ticket 5456]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The branch to [[!tails_gitweb_branch 5588-no-autologin-consoles desc=\"stop "
"creating auto-login text consoles\"]] was merged ([[!tails_ticket 5588]])."
msgstr ""
"شاخهٔ [[!tails_gitweb_branch 5588-no-autologin-consoles desc=\"توقف ایجاد "
"کنسول‌های متنی ورود خودکار\"]] ادغام شد ([[!tails_ticket 5588]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Support for persistence of I2P state was [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv "
"feature/i2p-persistence desc=\"drafted\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 5544]])."
msgstr ""
"پشتیبانی از وضعیت I2P مانا [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv feature/i2p-"
"persistence desc=\"پیش‌نویس شد\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 5544]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The website [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/cleanup-ikiwiki-setup desc=\"lock "
"down\"]] was merged and deployed."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/cleanup-ikiwiki-setup desc=\"قفل\"]] تارنما "
"ادغام و اجرا شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"A branch to [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/6790-remove-cookie-monster "
"desc=\"stop installing Cookie Monster\"]] was prepared ([[!tails_ticket "
"6790]])."
msgstr ""
"شاخهٔ [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/6790-remove-cookie-monster desc=\"توقف "
"نصب Cookie Monster\"]] آماده شد ([[!tails_ticket 6790]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some initial work to improve the Greeter's administration password interface "
"was done ([[!tails_ticket 5594]])."
msgstr ""
"کارهایی مقدماتی برای بهبود رابط گذرواژهٔ مدیریتی خوشامدگو انجام شدند ([["
"!tails_ticket 5594]])."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Software updates:"
msgstr "ارتقاهای نرم‌افزاری:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "I2P has been updated to 0.9.11 ([[!tails_ticket 6696]])."
msgstr "I2P به ۰٫۹٫۱۱ ارتقاء داده شد ([[!tails_ticket 6696]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"We have uploaded Pidgin 2.10.9 to squeeze-backports, and we now install it "
"from there ([[!tails_ticket 6661]])."
msgstr ""
"پیجین ۲٫۱۰٫۹ را به squeeze-backports آپلود کرده‌ایم و حالا آن را از آن‌جا "
"نصب می‌کنیم ([[!tails_ticket 6661]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Install [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/poedit-from-backports desc=\"Poedit "
"from squeeze-backports-sloppy\"]], where we have uploaded it some time ago "
"([[!tails_ticket 6456]])."
msgstr ""
"نصب [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/poedit-from-backports desc=\"Poedit از "
"squeeze-backports-sloppy\"]] که کمی پیش آن‌جا آپلود کرده بودیم ([["
"!tails_ticket 6456]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The fact that Linux 3.12 is not in Debian unstable anymore "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix/linux-kbuild-3.12-from-testing desc=\"was "
"taken into account\"]]."
msgstr ""
"این که لینوکس ۳٫۱۲ دیگر در دبیان ناپایدار نیست [[!tails_gitweb_branch bugfix"
"/linux-kbuild-3.12-from-testing desc=\"در نظر گرفته شد\"]]."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/linux-3.13 desc=\"branch\"]] that "
"installs Linux 3.13 was updated."
msgstr ""
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/linux-3.13 desc=\"شاخه‌ای\"]] که لینوکس ۳٫۱۳ "
"را نصب می‌کند ارتقاء داده‌شد."

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Bug and regression fixes:"
msgstr "رفع ایرادها و رگرسیون‌ها:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The Intel Management Engine Interface driver [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"feature/disable-mei desc=\"was disabled\"]]. This fixes memory wiping at "
"shutdown ([[!tails_ticket 6460]]) on some, if not all, hardware."
msgstr ""
"راه‌انداز رابط موتور مدیریت اینتل [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/disable-mei "
"desc=\"غیرفعال شد\"]]. این کار مشکل مربوط به پاک کردن حافظه هنگام خاموش کردن "
"را ([[!tails_ticket 6460]]) دست‌کم روی بعضی سخت‌افزارها حل می‌کند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The possibility to switch identities in the Tor Browser "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch_winterfairy bugfix/torbutton-new-identity desc=\"was "
"added back\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 6383]])."
msgstr ""
"احتمال تغییر هویت‌ها در مرورگر تور [[!tails_gitweb_branch_winterfairy bugfix"
"/torbutton-new-identity desc=\"دوباره اضافه شد\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 6383]])."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "An issue that lead to releasing needlessly big ISO images"
msgstr "مشکلی که منجر به انتشار تصاویر بی‌دلیل  بزرگ ایزو می‌شد"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  bugfix/6390-dont-include-APT-lists-and-cache-in-the-ISO desc=\"was\n"
"  resolved\"]] ([[!tails_ticket 6390]]).\n"
"- [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/create-additional-software-config]]\n"
"  was merged.\n"
msgstr ""
"  bugfix/6390-dont-include-APT-lists-and-cache-in-the-ISO desc=\"برطرف شد\"]]"
" ([[!tails_ticket 6390]]).\n"
"- [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/create-additional-software-config]]\n"
"  ادغام شد.\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid "Towards Tails based on Debian Wheezy:"
msgstr "پیش به سوی تیلز مبتنی بر Debian Wheezy:"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"I2P packages compatible with Debian Wheezy were prepared, and are now "
"installed in the [[!tails_gitweb_branch feature/wheezy]] branch."
msgstr ""
"بسته‌های I2P سازگار با Debian Wheezy آماده شده‌اند و حالا در شاخهٔ [["
"!tails_gitweb_branch feature/wheezy]] نصب می‌شوند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "Application launchers were added to the GNOME panel."
msgstr "راه‌اندازهای ابزارها به پنل گنوم اضافه شدند."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"A launcher to start the documentation viewer was added to the applications "
"menu."
msgstr "راه‌اندازی برای شروع بازدیدگر مستندات به فهرست ابزارها اضافه شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "A more standard icon is used for the shutdown button."
msgstr "یک نمایهٔ استانداردتر برای دکمهٔ خاموش انتخاب شد."

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Documentation, website and localization\n"
msgstr "مستندات، تارنما و بومی‌سازی\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"- Icons for the different roles on the Contribute section were\n"
"  finalized and [[deployed live|contribute]].\n"
"- The [[blueprint/FAQ]] was greatly expanded, and is now almost ready\n"
"  for prime-time.\n"
"- We have made good progress on specifying how the Tails logo should\n"
"  look like ([[!tails_ticket 5797]]).\n"
"- It was documented how to [[improve Tails by working on\n"
"  Debian|contribute/how/debian]]. We have received positive feedback\n"
"  from Debian contributors about it.\n"
"- Many small improvements to the documentation and its translations\n"
"  were done, including:\n"
"  * quite a few clarifications in the documentation for new\n"
"    contributors;\n"
"  * [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/system_requirements_improvements\n"
"    desc=\"updated\"]] system requirements documentation;\n"
"  * [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/change_persistence_passphrase\n"
"    desc=\"documented\"]] how to change the passphrase for the\n"
"    persistent volume ([[!tails_ticket 5621]]).\n"
"- Links to the I2P website were [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv\n"
"  bugfix/new-i2p-site desc=\"updated\"]].\n"
"- Documentation for the new MAC address spoofing feature was drafted.\n"
"- Work is in progress on documentation about contributing to Tails in\n"
"  the infrastructure (systems administration, automation) area.\n"
msgstr ""
"- نمایه‌های نقش‌های متفاوت در بخش همکاری\n"
"  نهایی شده و [[به کار برده شدند|contribute]].\n"
"- [[blueprint/FAQ]] تا حدود خوبی گسترش یافت و حالا دیگر \n"
"  برای استفادهٔ نهایی آماده است.\n"
"- پیشرفت خوبی در مشخص کردن شرایط لوگوی تیلز\n"
"  داشته‌ایم ([[!tails_ticket 5797]]).\n"
"- نحوهٔ [[پیشبرد تیلز با کار روی\n"
"  دبیان|contribute/how/debian]] مستندسازی شد. از مشارکت‌کنندگان دبیان\n"
"  بازخورد خوبی در مورد آن گرفتیم.\n"
"- پیشرفت‌های کوچک بسیاری در مستندات و ترجمه‌های آن‌ها\n"
"  به وجود آمدند، از جمله:\n"
"  * روشن کردن بعضی نکات برای مشارکت‌کنندگان\n"
"    جدید؛\n"
"  * [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/system_requirements_improvements\n"
"    desc=\"به‌روزرسانی\"]] مستندسازی نیازمندی‌های سیستم؛\n"
"  * [[!tails_gitweb_branch doc/change_persistence_passphrase\n"
"    desc=\"مستندسازی\"]] نحوهٔ تغییر گذرواژه برای\n"
"    درایو مانا ([[!tails_ticket 5621]]).\n"
"- پیوندها به تارنمای I2P  [[!tails_gitweb_branch_kytv\n"
"  bugfix/new-i2p-site desc=\"به‌روز شدند\"]].\n"
"- مستندات ویژگی جدید جا زدن آدرس مک پیش‌نویس شدند.\n"
"- کار مستندسازی همکاری با تیلز در مورد زیرساخت\n"
"   (مدیریت سیستم، خودکارسازی) در حال انجام است.\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "Infrastructure\n"
msgstr "زیرساخت\n"

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Our Puppet modules were [published](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/).  This "
"was a first blocker before we can welcome contributions to our "
"infrastructure."
msgstr ""
"مدول‌های پاپت ما [منتشر شدند](https://git-tails.immerda.ch/). این اولین کار "
"پیش از این بود که بتوانیم از همکاری در زمینهٔ زیرساخت‌های خود استقبال کنیم."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"The system that hosts our [[!tails_redmine \"\" desc=\"Redmine\"]] was "
"re-installed from scratch on a new machine, upgraded to Debian Wheezy and to "
"Redmine 1.4.4."
msgstr ""
"سیستمی که میزبان [[!tails_redmine \"\" desc=\"ردماین\"]] ما است از ابتدا روی "
"یک ماشین جدید نصب شده و به Debian Wheezy و نیز ردماین ۱٫۴٫۴ ارتقاء داده شد."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid ""
"Some improvements to our automated test suite were merged: "
"[[!tails_gitweb_branch test/fix-persistence-checks]], [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/keep-volumes-tag]], and [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/5959-antitest-memory-erasure]].  Thanks to this and the robustness "
"improvements brought by the move to RJB, we were finally able to remove two "
"of the most painful sets of tests from our manual test suite."
msgstr ""
"بهبودهایی در رابطه با بستهٔ آزمایشی خودکار ما ادغام شدند: [["
"!tails_gitweb_branch test/fix-persistence-checks]]، [[!tails_gitweb_branch "
"test/keep-volumes-tag]]، و [[!tails_gitweb_branch test/5959-antitest-memory-"
"erasure]]. با این کار و قدرت بهبودهایی که کوچ به RJB در اختیارمان گذاشته "
"بالاخره توانستیم دو مجموعه از آزمون‌های آزاردهندهٔ مجموعهٔ آزمایشی دستی‌مان "
"را حذف کنیم."

#. type: Bullet: '- '
msgid "A mailing-list for early testers was created and is being set up."
msgstr ""
"یک فهرست رایانامه برای آزمایش‌کنندگان اولیه ایجاد شد و در حال آماده شدن است."

